程序包 org.snt.inmemantlr.exceptions

  • 异常错误概要 
    异常错误 说明
    CompilationErrorException
    this exception is thrown when the compilation fails
    CompilationException  
    DeserializationException
    this exception is thrown when deserialization fails
    FileExistsException  
    IllegalWorkflowException
    this exception is thrown when an illegal workflow for the generic parser is encountered
    InjectionException
    this exception is something is going wrong when injecting subtree into AST
    ParseTreeProcessorException
    this exception is something is going wrong while processing an AST
    ParsingException
    this exception is thrown when a parsing error occurrs
    RedundantCompilationException
    this exception is thrown if the objects to be compiled are already compiled
    SerializationException
    this exception is thrown when serialization fails
